
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dr. Freddy Nadjingar Doumde | AI & Health Portfolio</title>

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #0f766e;
            --secondary: #4338ca;
            --accent: #8b5cf6;
            --bg-light: #f8fafc;
            --text-dark: #0f172a;
            --text-muted: #475569;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --gradient-main: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            --gradient-text: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--accent));
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            background: var(--bg-light);
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 100px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>✅ Ton site fonctionne correctement 🎉</h1>

</body>
</html>
